WEBVTT

01:30.920 --> 01:35.009
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.900 --> 01:39.450
[1998]

01:36.000 --> 01:36.560
Xiaolan,

01:37.280 --> 01:38.350
look what I made.

01:39.000 --> 01:40.680
Ribs, your favorite.

01:41.680 --> 01:42.210
Xiaolan,

01:42.740 --> 01:44.740
wash your hands and get ready to eat.

02:08.590 --> 02:09.120
Xiaolan!

02:10.560 --> 02:11.090
Xiaolan!

02:12.560 --> 02:13.800
Why did you come here instead of

02:13.800 --> 02:15.200
going home after school?

02:15.280 --> 02:17.000
Are you trying to scare me to death?

02:17.000 --> 02:18.400
I'm sorry, Auntie.

02:18.680 --> 02:21.030
I miss Mom and Dad.

02:26.280 --> 02:27.280
Silly child.

02:28.430 --> 02:30.120
Your parents are gone,

02:30.910 --> 02:33.110
but you still have your own life to live.

02:33.840 --> 02:34.710
You need to

02:35.360 --> 02:37.220
live your life well, step by step.

02:37.470 --> 02:38.280
Understand?

02:45.170 --> 02:47.740
[Episode 8: Every Step in Life]

03:22.400 --> 03:23.200
They are here!

03:24.960 --> 03:25.829
Silly boy!

03:27.630 --> 03:28.120
Mom.

03:29.000 --> 03:29.590
Mom!

03:30.190 --> 03:31.590
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

03:43.310 --> 03:45.030
Everyone, quiet down please!

03:47.100 --> 03:48.360
[Warm congratulations to Xia Xiaolan,
a villager from Qijing Village,]

03:47.680 --> 03:48.710
Let me say a few words.

03:48.360 --> 03:49.620
[for becoming the top scorer in the
college entrance exam in Yunan Province]

03:49.360 --> 03:51.190
I'm very happy today.

03:51.400 --> 03:53.190
Our village has never had

03:53.560 --> 03:54.840
a top scorer before.

03:55.190 --> 03:57.630
But today, Xiaolan did it.

03:57.800 --> 03:59.750
Aren't we all happy?

03:59.840 --> 04:02.080
Yes!

04:03.680 --> 04:05.140
And Chen Qing did well too.

04:05.190 --> 04:06.360
With over 500 points,

04:06.360 --> 04:08.430
he can also get into
a university in Jingcheng.

04:08.430 --> 04:09.960
Xiaolan is our "top scholar,"

04:09.960 --> 04:10.750
and Chen Qing

04:10.910 --> 04:12.520
is at least an "imperial scholar," right?

04:12.520 --> 04:13.630
Yes!

04:13.650 --> 04:14.340
Yes!

04:15.750 --> 04:16.160
Yes!

04:17.120 --> 04:18.450
And I want to thank Chief

04:18.600 --> 04:20.870
for helping us
move our household registration back.

04:20.870 --> 04:22.120
And I want to thank

04:22.190 --> 04:23.830
all the uncles and aunties in the village

04:23.830 --> 04:25.340
for taking care of us.

04:25.430 --> 04:26.600
Thank you.

04:26.630 --> 04:27.240
Thank you.

04:27.240 --> 04:28.120
Such a good kid.

04:28.870 --> 04:30.270
Chen Qing and Xiaolan

04:30.680 --> 04:32.280
are the pride of our village.

04:32.750 --> 04:34.800
The slogan on this wall says it well:

04:35.070 --> 04:37.000
"Knowledge can change your life."

04:37.320 --> 04:38.290
I hope you all

04:38.510 --> 04:39.920
learn from them,

04:40.159 --> 04:41.310
study hard

04:41.659 --> 04:42.750
and get into universities—

04:42.750 --> 04:44.000
good universities!

04:44.750 --> 04:45.870
All parents

04:46.040 --> 04:47.920
should support their children.

04:48.070 --> 04:49.190
Both boys and girls

04:49.360 --> 04:50.780
should be allowed to go to school

04:50.780 --> 04:51.390
and study.

04:51.630 --> 04:53.230
If your family has any difficulties,

04:53.230 --> 04:54.630
please speak up.

04:55.040 --> 04:57.110
The village will help.

04:57.360 --> 04:59.310
Bravo!

04:59.560 --> 05:01.040
Xiaolan is amazing.

05:01.630 --> 05:02.720
These children...

05:02.830 --> 05:04.680
have been through so much.

05:04.920 --> 05:05.650
Alright now.

05:05.870 --> 05:07.160
On such a happy day,

05:07.430 --> 05:08.950
let's not shed tears.

05:09.310 --> 05:10.750
I am just happy.

05:10.950 --> 05:11.630
Yes, yes.

05:11.950 --> 05:13.070
Everyone,

05:13.070 --> 05:14.630
come to our house for drinks tonight!

05:14.630 --> 05:16.720
Great!

05:17.040 --> 05:18.190
Everyone come!

05:30.700 --> 05:31.800
Although you didn't pass this year,

05:31.800 --> 05:33.000
you'll definitely get in next year.

05:33.000 --> 05:33.930
I had a good time.

05:35.040 --> 05:36.270
Study hard, okay?

05:36.270 --> 05:37.040
Be careful on the way home.

05:37.040 --> 05:39.300
Learn from Xiaolan and get into college.

05:39.510 --> 05:40.750
Uncle Yong, don't worry!

05:40.750 --> 05:42.950
I'll definitely work harder next year.

05:43.510 --> 05:45.159
Okay. Thank you.

05:45.480 --> 05:46.720
What a happy day.

05:46.720 --> 05:47.159
Fen,

05:47.390 --> 05:47.950
Xiaolan.

05:48.070 --> 05:49.240
Get some rest early.

05:49.560 --> 05:49.920
Okay.

05:49.920 --> 05:51.600
Fen, don't bother cleaning up today.

05:51.600 --> 05:52.530
It's too tiring.

05:52.680 --> 05:53.159
Get some rest early.

05:53.159 --> 05:54.260
Your brother is drunk.

05:54.260 --> 05:55.300
Who's drunk?

05:55.480 --> 05:57.040
I can walk in a straight line.

05:57.040 --> 05:58.770
That's enough. Get inside now.

06:00.950 --> 06:01.560
Xiaolan.

06:02.430 --> 06:03.270
Well...

06:04.160 --> 06:05.760
I need to tell you something.

06:05.870 --> 06:06.920
Don't be mad.

06:08.190 --> 06:09.190
On the day

06:09.830 --> 06:11.000
Xia Dajun got the divorce certificate,

06:11.000 --> 06:11.860
he disappeared

06:12.480 --> 06:14.680
and there's been no word from him since.

06:16.270 --> 06:16.750
Mom,

06:17.240 --> 06:17.950
I'm not mad.

06:18.800 --> 06:19.430
I know

06:19.950 --> 06:21.160
you're not being foolish

06:21.160 --> 06:22.630
and thinking about the Xia family

06:22.630 --> 06:24.120
or holding onto Xia Dajun.

06:25.070 --> 06:26.270
You're just too kind.

06:27.190 --> 06:28.270
Usually, you even show concern

06:28.270 --> 06:29.070
for strangers

06:29.240 --> 06:30.700
when they suffer a little—

06:30.950 --> 06:31.830
let alone

06:32.270 --> 06:32.950
your ex‑husband,

06:32.950 --> 06:35.010
whom you lived with for so many years.

06:35.600 --> 06:37.510
I just wanted to tell him

06:38.070 --> 06:40.200
that you got into Huaqing University.

06:40.390 --> 06:41.450
I didn't expect...

06:42.560 --> 06:44.870
the Xia family to be in such chaos now.

06:45.510 --> 06:46.800
I guess this is karma.

06:48.159 --> 06:49.270
Alright, stop thinking about it anymore.

06:49.270 --> 06:50.070
Let's go home.

06:50.120 --> 06:50.650
Xiaolan!

06:51.430 --> 06:51.960
Xiaolan!

06:52.070 --> 06:53.270
You have a phone call!

06:53.570 --> 06:54.270
It's at the village committee.

06:54.270 --> 06:54.720
Go now.

06:54.720 --> 06:55.120
Okay.

06:55.240 --> 06:56.300
Thank you, Auntie.

06:56.710 --> 06:57.430
This child...

06:57.430 --> 06:58.360
Such a good girl.

06:59.159 --> 06:59.760
Mrs. Chen,

07:00.310 --> 07:01.510
who called her?

07:02.950 --> 07:04.810
I was in such a hurry to come get her

07:05.000 --> 07:06.130
that I forgot to ask.

07:07.600 --> 07:08.480
How did these two kids

07:08.480 --> 07:09.430
turn out to be so outstanding?

07:09.430 --> 07:11.490
Yes, yes. Chen Qing is excellent too.

07:14.000 --> 07:14.480
Hello?

07:14.560 --> 07:15.520
Congratulations,

07:15.520 --> 07:16.430
Xia Xiaolan,

07:16.680 --> 07:19.070
for becoming
the top science student in Yunan.

07:19.070 --> 07:19.800
Thank you.

07:20.160 --> 07:21.190
How did you do?

07:22.680 --> 07:24.270
I can't compare myself

07:24.270 --> 07:26.070
with the provincial top scorer,

07:26.120 --> 07:26.800
but...

07:27.120 --> 07:27.720
I should be able

07:27.720 --> 07:29.250
to get into Huaqing as well.

07:29.430 --> 07:31.030
I can be your schoolmate now.

07:32.830 --> 07:33.510
Xiaolan,

07:34.240 --> 07:35.440
what gift do you want?

07:35.980 --> 07:37.570
My college entrance exam score

07:37.570 --> 07:38.970
is already the best gift.

07:40.390 --> 07:42.320
I'm talking about a birthday gift.

07:43.240 --> 07:43.720
What?

07:44.240 --> 07:44.920
Don't tell me you're so happy

07:44.920 --> 07:46.750
that you've forgotten your own birthday.

07:46.750 --> 07:47.630
My birthday?

07:48.240 --> 07:49.510
This is your first birthday

07:49.510 --> 07:50.950
since we've known each other.

07:50.950 --> 07:51.870
I wanted

07:51.870 --> 07:53.130
to give you a surprise,

07:53.390 --> 07:54.390
but then I thought

07:54.920 --> 07:56.480
it would be better to give you something

07:56.480 --> 07:57.340
you truly like.

07:57.950 --> 07:58.950
Anything is fine,

07:59.120 --> 08:00.360
as long as
you don't pack yourself in a box

08:00.360 --> 08:01.870
and send yourself over.

08:03.920 --> 08:04.920
That's an option?

08:05.120 --> 08:05.920
Just kidding.

08:05.920 --> 08:07.250
Don't actually do that.

08:07.680 --> 08:08.410
Maybe I will.

08:08.950 --> 08:10.750
Your gift will arrive next week.

08:10.830 --> 08:11.190
Okay.

08:11.800 --> 08:12.800
See you next week.

08:18.600 --> 08:19.720
See you next week?

08:21.510 --> 08:22.920
Can you finally tell me

08:23.830 --> 08:25.680
why you've been going to Yunan?

08:28.120 --> 08:29.240
Director Guan, you've probably wanted

08:29.240 --> 08:30.390
to ask this for a long time, right?

08:30.390 --> 08:31.510
You must be dying to know.

08:31.510 --> 08:32.630
Of course.

08:33.600 --> 08:35.400
Didn't I want you
to focus on the college entrance exam?

08:35.400 --> 08:36.510
Now that the exam is over

08:36.510 --> 08:37.480
and the celebration's done,

08:37.480 --> 08:38.600
don't you think

08:38.600 --> 08:40.000
you owe your mom a report?

08:40.390 --> 08:40.919
Alright.

08:41.080 --> 08:42.440
Well then, Director Guan,

08:42.440 --> 08:43.840
I'll give you the report.

08:44.820 --> 08:47.350
Her name is Xia Xiaolan.

08:48.200 --> 08:50.550
She's from Qijing Village, Yunan Province.

08:50.550 --> 08:52.270
She took the college entrance exam
with me this year

08:52.270 --> 08:54.730
and became
the top science student in Yunan.

08:55.840 --> 08:57.550
She's been admitted to Huaqing University,

08:57.550 --> 08:58.870
majoring in Architecture,

08:58.870 --> 09:00.600
and will soon be my schoolmate.

09:02.190 --> 09:03.340
The English study tips

09:03.340 --> 09:04.550
posted on the wall

09:04.550 --> 09:05.840
in front of your desk...

09:05.840 --> 09:07.320
they're hers, right?

09:07.320 --> 09:08.380
Yes, that's right.

09:08.510 --> 09:09.630
If she hadn't helped me improve my English

09:09.630 --> 09:10.600
by over 30 points,

09:10.600 --> 09:12.660
I might not have been admitted at all.

09:13.630 --> 09:15.430
She, a kid from the countryside,

09:16.630 --> 09:19.150
became the top science student
in her province?

09:19.150 --> 09:20.190
First in Yunan,

09:20.440 --> 09:21.700
and 3rd in the country.

09:22.870 --> 09:23.600
Impressive.

09:24.270 --> 09:26.120
Actually, I made up my mind

09:26.120 --> 09:27.120
to repeat a year

09:27.500 --> 09:29.230
because of her encouragement.

09:29.390 --> 09:29.960
I admit

09:30.580 --> 09:32.350
I have feelings for her.

09:32.960 --> 09:34.890
And I expressed my feelings to her.

09:35.150 --> 09:35.870
But...

09:36.030 --> 09:37.090
she turned me down.

09:38.750 --> 09:39.880
I really admire her.

09:40.080 --> 09:41.480
She didn't say yes

09:41.600 --> 09:42.790
because of my background.

09:42.790 --> 09:44.200
Instead, she chose to rely on herself—

09:44.200 --> 09:45.260
and she succeeded.

09:46.150 --> 09:48.080
So I have to keep working hard

09:48.080 --> 09:49.140
to be worthy of her.

09:50.240 --> 09:51.840
How are you not worthy of her?

09:52.380 --> 09:53.960
Let's not even mention you were born
into the Zhou family.

09:53.960 --> 09:54.480
Right?

09:54.870 --> 09:56.270
You got into Huaqing

09:56.270 --> 09:57.440
on your own ability.

09:57.600 --> 09:59.120
The top scorer

09:59.390 --> 10:01.240
only beat you by a few points.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.080
How did my son end up

10:02.080 --> 10:03.510
losing confidence because of that?
Seriously.

10:03.510 --> 10:04.240
Mom.

10:05.120 --> 10:06.960
It's precisely because
I was born into the Zhou family

10:06.960 --> 10:08.550
that I feel I'm not worthy of her.

10:08.550 --> 10:09.080
Look,

10:09.550 --> 10:11.440
our family gave me such good conditions,

10:11.440 --> 10:11.910
so my starting point

10:11.910 --> 10:13.480
was higher than many people's.

10:13.480 --> 10:14.540
But what about her?

10:14.720 --> 10:16.320
She was born in the countryside,

10:16.320 --> 10:17.230
with tough

10:17.270 --> 10:18.470
material conditions

10:18.510 --> 10:20.040
and learning environment.

10:20.240 --> 10:21.200
And in her family,

10:21.200 --> 10:22.270
there are...

10:23.510 --> 10:24.040
In short,

10:24.640 --> 10:26.170
she must've put in hundreds

10:26.180 --> 10:27.720
or thousands of times more effort

10:27.720 --> 10:28.920
than I did to get here.

10:29.240 --> 10:30.080
So she's...

10:30.750 --> 10:31.630
smarter...

10:32.870 --> 10:33.930
and braver than me.

10:36.240 --> 10:37.750
Do you know how happy I am

10:37.750 --> 10:39.030
to hear you say that?

10:40.580 --> 10:41.230
Looks like

10:42.000 --> 10:43.800
you're serious about this girl.

11:05.200 --> 11:06.730
So your birthday is in July.

11:07.360 --> 11:08.960
I wonder if you're satisfied

11:09.470 --> 11:11.470
with the time we've spent together.

11:12.910 --> 11:14.600
I increasingly want

11:15.510 --> 11:17.240
to carry both our courage

11:17.240 --> 11:18.000
and dreams

11:19.360 --> 11:20.000
and see

11:20.600 --> 11:21.600
how far I can go.

11:30.360 --> 11:31.690
Be careful, be careful.

11:32.080 --> 11:33.390
Take a break if you're tired. Be careful.

11:33.390 --> 11:34.480
Don't force yourself.

11:34.480 --> 11:35.360
Be careful. Be careful.

11:35.360 --> 11:36.910
Stop hanging onto me.

11:37.150 --> 11:38.120
You might as well help me

11:38.120 --> 11:38.910
carry the TV.

11:38.910 --> 11:40.240
Alright. I'll carry both you and the TV.

11:40.240 --> 11:41.120
Come on. Hurry.

11:41.200 --> 11:41.670
Careful.

11:41.670 --> 11:42.120
Alright. Alright.

11:42.120 --> 11:43.000
Easy, easy, easy.

11:43.000 --> 11:44.080
Careful now.

11:45.550 --> 11:46.680
-Okay.
-Be careful.

11:46.910 --> 11:47.550
Come on, straighten it.

11:47.550 --> 11:48.440
Turn it around.

11:48.840 --> 11:49.700
Straighten it.

11:50.240 --> 11:50.900
Take a look.

11:51.240 --> 11:51.870
Dayong.

11:52.390 --> 11:52.790
Thanks for your hard work.

11:52.790 --> 11:53.960
Your relative is here.

11:53.960 --> 11:55.620
He's waiting at the entrance.

11:57.090 --> 11:58.140
I'll go check.

11:58.480 --> 11:59.010
Go ahead.

12:00.140 --> 12:01.410
Listen,

12:01.630 --> 12:03.560
your job is just to keep an eye on it.

12:03.630 --> 12:05.160
Don't let anyone get close.

12:14.630 --> 12:15.960
What are you looking at?

12:17.670 --> 12:18.080
Uncle.

12:18.910 --> 12:19.970
Don't call me that.

12:22.080 --> 12:23.550
How long have you been here?

12:23.550 --> 12:24.880
J-just arrived, Uncle.

12:26.320 --> 12:27.240
Just arrived?

12:31.840 --> 12:32.910
Mr. Zhou.

12:34.440 --> 12:36.240
Did you get into college?

12:36.360 --> 12:37.000
I did.

12:37.550 --> 12:39.010
Huaqing, majoring in Law.

12:40.630 --> 12:42.030
You got into Huaqing too?

12:43.360 --> 12:45.320
That's impressive! Amazing!

12:47.390 --> 12:48.240
Our Xiaolan

12:48.630 --> 12:50.510
is Yunan's top scorer!

12:51.020 --> 12:52.080
She even went on TV

12:52.080 --> 12:53.150
for an interview.

12:53.350 --> 12:54.880
We've already set up the TV.

12:55.030 --> 12:56.120
The whole village is coming tonight

12:56.120 --> 12:58.000
to watch her interview.

12:58.170 --> 12:59.510
You've arrived just in time.

12:59.510 --> 13:00.970
Join us and learn from her.

13:01.390 --> 13:01.840
Okay.

13:04.030 --> 13:05.430
What's that in your hand?

13:06.440 --> 13:07.000
This...

13:07.150 --> 13:08.880
is a birthday cake for Xiaolan.

13:13.840 --> 13:14.510
Their shop

13:14.510 --> 13:15.440
is closing soon,

13:16.150 --> 13:17.480
and she'll be back then.

13:18.270 --> 13:19.270
Thank you, Uncle.

13:19.960 --> 13:21.220
Stop calling me Uncle.

13:25.440 --> 13:26.270
Alright.

13:26.910 --> 13:27.440
It's lit.

13:29.750 --> 13:32.240
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

13:29.810 --> 13:30.500
Ready—

13:32.680 --> 13:35.390
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

13:35.750 --> 13:38.870
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

13:39.080 --> 13:42.000
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

13:49.630 --> 13:50.870
I hope everyone I love

13:51.440 --> 13:52.320
can be happy.

13:57.910 --> 13:58.840
Happy birthday.

13:58.840 --> 14:00.510
-Happy birthday.
-Happy birthday.

14:00.510 --> 14:01.960
Can we eat the cake now?

14:02.150 --> 14:04.440
This cake from the city is so pretty!

14:04.630 --> 14:05.670
If you behave well,

14:05.670 --> 14:07.670
I'll buy you one next time
I go to the city.

14:07.670 --> 14:08.870
Xiaolan, ignore him.

14:08.960 --> 14:10.960
Whatever's next? Please continue.

14:11.360 --> 14:13.670
The next thing on the agenda is...

14:15.270 --> 14:16.230
eating cake!

14:17.870 --> 14:18.320
Here.

14:29.840 --> 14:31.870
Let's give the biggest piece

14:32.000 --> 14:32.810
to Tao!

14:33.240 --> 14:34.200
Come on. What should you say?

14:34.200 --> 14:35.320
Thank you, Xiaolan!

14:35.320 --> 14:36.630
Happy birthday, Xiaolan.

14:36.630 --> 14:37.960
May you live a long life!

14:38.390 --> 14:40.050
And I hope you grow up healthy!

14:47.080 --> 14:47.870
This piece

14:48.510 --> 14:49.370
is for you, Mom.

14:50.360 --> 14:52.240
Mom, you gave birth to me and raised me.

14:52.240 --> 14:53.840
Thank you for your hard work.

14:54.550 --> 14:55.750
It wasn't hard for me.

14:56.600 --> 14:57.080
Eat up.

15:06.870 --> 15:07.390
Uncle.

15:07.390 --> 15:07.960
Alright.

15:08.320 --> 15:08.870
Auntie.

15:11.750 --> 15:13.210
Thank you for taking us in.

15:14.150 --> 15:15.360
This place

15:15.750 --> 15:16.670
is not just a shelter

15:16.670 --> 15:18.270
from the wind and rain for me.

15:19.510 --> 15:20.390
It's my home.

15:22.080 --> 15:22.750
Xiaolan,

15:23.630 --> 15:24.690
what you're saying

15:24.840 --> 15:26.150
is making me cry.

15:26.150 --> 15:26.550
Yes.

15:26.550 --> 15:28.550
Family doesn't need to be so formal.

15:31.440 --> 15:32.000
Eat up.

15:39.600 --> 15:42.870
This piece is for you, Zhou Cheng.

15:42.870 --> 15:43.470
Thank you.

15:44.240 --> 15:44.900
Uncle Yong.

15:45.790 --> 15:46.650
Go watch the TV.

15:46.670 --> 15:48.790
Xiaolan's interview is about to start.

15:48.790 --> 15:49.840
Let's go, hurry!

15:49.960 --> 15:50.360
Let's go!

15:50.360 --> 15:51.080
Let's go over there!

15:51.080 --> 15:52.000
Or we'll miss it.

15:52.000 --> 15:52.440
Xiaolan...

15:52.440 --> 15:53.150
Coming!

15:53.390 --> 15:53.790
Hurry!

16:15.840 --> 16:17.240
In this year's college entrance exam,

16:17.240 --> 16:18.080
Xia Xiaolan
from Anqing County No.1 High School

16:18.080 --> 16:19.170
achieved

16:19.200 --> 16:20.960
the top science score in Yunan Province

16:20.960 --> 16:22.810
with 616 points.

16:22.960 --> 16:24.000
We rushed over

16:24.000 --> 16:25.630
to interview her on the spot.

16:26.840 --> 16:28.440
First, let's congratulate Xia

16:28.440 --> 16:29.790
on this outstanding achievement.

16:29.790 --> 16:30.920
Isn't that Xiaolan?

16:32.840 --> 16:33.510
Xia.

16:34.150 --> 16:34.790
So pretty!

16:35.480 --> 16:36.150
Xiaolan!

16:36.870 --> 16:37.360
Mom!

16:37.390 --> 16:39.150
Xiaolan is on TV!

16:39.170 --> 16:40.570
Yes, there she is.

16:41.030 --> 16:42.030
Study hard,

16:42.080 --> 16:44.000
and you can be on TV when you grow up.

16:44.000 --> 16:45.070
Quiet, everyone.

16:45.200 --> 16:46.120
Please be quiet.

16:46.120 --> 16:47.360
I can't hear Xiaolan.

16:47.440 --> 16:48.370
Please be quiet.

16:49.670 --> 16:51.670
I want to thank my teachers
for their guidance

16:51.670 --> 16:53.530
and my classmates for their help.

16:53.840 --> 16:55.240
My achievement today

16:55.510 --> 16:57.040
didn't come out of nowhere.

16:57.050 --> 16:57.850
Without them,

16:57.870 --> 16:59.400
I wouldn't be who I am today.

16:59.720 --> 17:01.750
How thoughtful this kid is!

17:01.750 --> 17:02.270
Right?

17:02.630 --> 17:03.790
Good girl!

17:04.730 --> 17:05.410
Xia,

17:05.440 --> 17:06.920
why is your hand in a cast?

17:06.940 --> 17:08.069
Did you get injured?

17:08.680 --> 17:09.069
Yes.

17:09.310 --> 17:11.109
I got injured
before the college entrance exam,

17:11.109 --> 17:12.310
so I had to wear a cast.

17:12.829 --> 17:14.200
Because of that,

17:14.510 --> 17:16.640
my hand movement was limited,

17:17.160 --> 17:18.550
and I might not have done so well

17:18.550 --> 17:20.609
on some of the open-ended questions.

17:37.000 --> 17:38.440
Change the channel.

17:40.360 --> 17:42.240
How did you get injured before the exam?

17:42.240 --> 17:43.650
Was it an accident?

17:48.790 --> 17:50.720
Someone stepped on my wrist.

17:51.400 --> 17:53.600
I don't know if it counts as an accident.

18:01.880 --> 18:04.010
But fortunately, it didn't affect me.

18:04.110 --> 18:05.830
I also want to use this experience

18:05.830 --> 18:07.360
to tell everyone one thing:

18:08.480 --> 18:09.510
life

18:09.510 --> 18:11.160
is full of unexpected events.

18:11.160 --> 18:12.090
Don't be afraid,

18:12.240 --> 18:13.500
and don't shrink back.

18:13.550 --> 18:14.480
No matter when,

18:14.880 --> 18:16.720
we should always face problems bravely

18:16.720 --> 18:17.580
and solve them.

18:18.750 --> 18:19.920
Well said!

18:20.550 --> 18:21.350
Bravo!

18:21.550 --> 18:22.400
Bravo!

18:22.830 --> 18:23.440
This kid

18:23.440 --> 18:25.300
is truly the pride of our village!

18:44.720 --> 18:45.350
Xiaolan,

18:45.430 --> 18:46.640
you did so well on TV

18:46.640 --> 18:47.450
just now.

18:47.480 --> 18:48.160
Thank you.

19:03.750 --> 19:04.510
Xiaolan.

19:05.550 --> 19:06.440
So what are you

19:07.350 --> 19:08.480
planning to do next?

19:10.270 --> 19:10.870
I'll wait.

19:12.440 --> 19:14.640
The stone has been thrown into the pond,

19:15.000 --> 19:16.760
and the ripples need some time

19:16.790 --> 19:18.000
to reach the shore.

19:21.720 --> 19:23.640
So the words you didn't finish just now...

19:23.640 --> 19:25.970
someone is waiting for you to finish them.

19:29.480 --> 19:30.140
Zhou Cheng.

19:32.830 --> 19:34.640
What I was going to say is...

19:38.240 --> 19:38.840
thank you.

19:41.830 --> 19:42.430
That's it?

19:49.880 --> 19:51.540
You always say thank you to me,

19:52.440 --> 19:53.240
but actually,

19:54.720 --> 19:57.050
the one you should thank most is yourself.

19:57.640 --> 19:58.680
Because it's thanks to you,

19:58.680 --> 19:59.410
who are smart

19:59.960 --> 20:00.680
and brave,

20:01.960 --> 20:03.420
that those of us around you

20:04.070 --> 20:05.130
can become better.

20:06.640 --> 20:07.310
Actually,

20:08.160 --> 20:10.360
these past few days, I've been thinking

20:10.720 --> 20:12.250
about what gift to give you—

20:12.790 --> 20:13.550
a watch?

20:14.350 --> 20:15.350
Or maybe jewelry?

20:16.070 --> 20:17.470
No matter how expensive,

20:17.750 --> 20:20.080
it still felt like something was missing.

20:20.790 --> 20:21.510
So,

20:27.790 --> 20:28.920
I'm giving you this.

20:38.750 --> 20:39.240
I know

20:40.550 --> 20:41.350
you'll have

20:41.830 --> 20:43.160
an extraordinary life,

20:44.270 --> 20:45.130
and your future

20:45.590 --> 20:46.680
will certainly

20:46.680 --> 20:48.340
shine even brighter than now.

20:49.720 --> 20:50.980
Let this accompany you

20:51.240 --> 20:53.440
as you write your brilliant life story.

21:20.720 --> 21:22.830
This is the first real victory I've had

21:22.830 --> 21:24.350
since coming here,

21:25.200 --> 21:27.600
and the first time
I've truly freed myself.

21:28.480 --> 21:30.200
I hope my future life

21:30.880 --> 21:32.740
can shine as brightly as tonight.

21:37.440 --> 21:38.030
Fate,

21:39.160 --> 21:39.960
thank you,

21:40.200 --> 21:42.200
for giving me a chance to start over.

21:48.470 --> 21:49.470
And thank you too.

21:52.840 --> 21:53.710
The truth is,

21:54.510 --> 21:55.350
I can't

21:55.350 --> 21:56.590
keep denying that,

21:57.480 --> 21:59.810
without even realizing it, I have already

21:59.960 --> 22:01.030
been moved by him.

22:04.270 --> 22:05.720
If someone loves you,

22:06.360 --> 22:07.160
respects you,

22:07.720 --> 22:08.720
and protects you,

22:09.240 --> 22:11.110
who cares if it's a dream?

22:13.510 --> 22:14.170
Zhou Cheng.

22:16.480 --> 22:17.010
Xiaolan.

22:19.200 --> 22:19.880
Actually, I don't have

22:19.880 --> 22:21.280
much dating experience,

22:22.790 --> 22:24.200
and I never imagined

22:24.880 --> 22:26.340
I'd meet someone like you.

22:27.350 --> 22:28.810
But I promise, from now on,

22:29.510 --> 22:30.910
I won't run away anymore.

22:32.150 --> 22:33.100
So,

22:35.550 --> 22:37.160
should we give this a try?

22:42.830 --> 22:43.200
I...

22:43.200 --> 22:43.660
I agree.

22:54.460 --> 22:57.760
♪ I don't know when it started ♪

22:56.920 --> 22:57.920
Comrade Xiaolan,

22:58.200 --> 23:01.610
♪ But my world suddenly became bright ♪

22:59.440 --> 23:00.440
I will definitely

23:00.790 --> 23:01.720
take our relationship seriously.

23:01.630 --> 23:05.150
♪ In the second our eyes met ♪

23:04.200 --> 23:04.590
Okay.

23:06.490 --> 23:09.110
♪ I knew it had to be you ♪

23:07.790 --> 23:08.680
Well then,

23:09.790 --> 23:11.450
from now on, call me "Beauty."

23:15.480 --> 23:15.940
Beauty.

23:18.160 --> 23:18.680
Beauty.

23:29.880 --> 23:30.810
Xia Changzheng,

23:31.400 --> 23:33.000
I've asked you several times already.

23:33.000 --> 23:35.000
Why did Zhao Gang
and Zhao Yong attack you?

23:35.000 --> 23:35.930
Where's my hand?

23:36.750 --> 23:37.680
Where's my hand?

23:38.750 --> 23:39.680
Where's my hand?

23:40.450 --> 23:41.920
Calm down, Xia Changzheng.

23:41.920 --> 23:43.520
I can't live without my hand!

23:43.680 --> 23:45.600
My hand... My hand...

23:47.510 --> 23:48.480
My hand...

23:49.640 --> 23:50.070
My...

23:51.000 --> 23:51.880
Last night,

23:52.070 --> 23:53.870
Freckles Sun turned himself in.

23:53.880 --> 23:54.550
He said

23:55.030 --> 23:56.920
Xia Changzheng instigated him

23:57.590 --> 23:59.520
to come to your school and hurt you.

24:00.110 --> 24:02.750
The goal was to stop you from taking
the college entrance exam.

24:02.750 --> 24:04.350
Why did he suddenly confess?

24:05.750 --> 24:06.350
He said

24:06.960 --> 24:07.920
that now the whole village

24:07.920 --> 24:09.510
is talking about you every day.

24:09.510 --> 24:10.910
And after he saw you on TV,

24:11.200 --> 24:13.060
he thought you had become famous.

24:13.350 --> 24:15.280
No matter what you tell the police,

24:15.480 --> 24:16.810
we'd believe it anyway.

24:16.880 --> 24:18.310
Rather than staying at home
waiting to be caught,

24:18.310 --> 24:19.720
he thought it would be better
to turn himself in.

24:19.720 --> 24:21.160
The police rely on evidence.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.590
Although Xiaolan is famous now,

24:22.590 --> 24:24.520
it wouldn't affect your judgment.

24:24.920 --> 24:26.270
He was guilty

24:26.590 --> 24:28.050
and scared out of his mind.

24:28.400 --> 24:28.960
Later,

24:29.000 --> 24:30.140
we went to Dahe Village

24:30.140 --> 24:32.670
to get more information
from Xia Changzheng,

24:32.680 --> 24:33.740
but he wasn't home.

24:34.000 --> 24:34.640
We eventually

24:34.640 --> 24:35.680
found him

24:35.920 --> 24:36.720
in a haystack.

24:37.200 --> 24:38.960
His hand had already been cut.

24:39.500 --> 24:40.610
Zhao Yong

24:40.920 --> 24:42.720
and his brother Zhao Gang did it.

24:43.160 --> 24:44.200
Do you know them?

24:44.640 --> 24:45.750
Not really.

24:46.200 --> 24:47.160
We have a clothing store

24:47.160 --> 24:48.160
in Shangdu.

24:48.360 --> 24:50.220
They often come to cause trouble.

24:50.640 --> 24:51.640
That makes sense.

24:51.840 --> 24:53.790
He also took money from Xia Changzheng.

24:53.790 --> 24:54.680
It seems that

24:54.840 --> 24:56.970
Xia Changzheng didn't pay them later.

24:57.310 --> 24:59.000
When Zhao Yong learned that Xia Changzheng

24:59.000 --> 25:00.240
had sold the eatery

25:00.270 --> 25:01.160
and made some money,

25:01.160 --> 25:02.420
he went to look for him,

25:02.480 --> 25:03.000
and

25:03.110 --> 25:04.710
they ended up having a fight.

25:06.200 --> 25:07.160
This Xia Changzheng

25:07.160 --> 25:08.450
is Xiaolan's uncle.

25:09.030 --> 25:10.160
Why does he keep doing

25:10.160 --> 25:10.960
these things?

25:11.280 --> 25:12.920
It's as if he doesn't want Xiaolan

25:12.920 --> 25:14.480
to study and take the exam.

25:14.880 --> 25:16.270
Now I finally know

25:16.550 --> 25:19.150
how the Xia family
has been harming my Xiaolan.

25:19.550 --> 25:20.640
I really regret

25:21.070 --> 25:22.830
being so blind for all these years.

25:22.830 --> 25:24.640
I should have left that family long ago.

25:24.640 --> 25:25.030
Mom,

25:25.640 --> 25:27.830
this matter is far beyond

25:27.830 --> 25:29.430
a simple family dispute now.

25:30.240 --> 25:31.160
The police

25:31.180 --> 25:32.440
will give us an answer.

25:32.960 --> 25:34.960
I just don't understand.

25:35.590 --> 25:36.960
When I transferred

25:37.070 --> 25:38.510
to Anqing No.1 High School,

25:38.510 --> 25:41.110
my parents had already been separated
for a long time,

25:41.110 --> 25:42.310
and I never spent a cent

25:42.310 --> 25:43.790
of my uncle's family's money
on my studies.

25:43.790 --> 25:45.400
Why would they try so hard to hurt me

25:45.400 --> 25:48.070
and stop me
from taking the college entrance exam?

25:48.070 --> 25:49.110
What motive

25:49.110 --> 25:50.570
could they possibly have?

25:50.790 --> 25:51.920
We want to

25:51.920 --> 25:52.790
know that too.

25:53.400 --> 25:53.960
But

25:54.310 --> 25:56.400
given Xia Changzheng's current condition,

25:56.400 --> 25:57.830
he can't confess anything.

25:57.830 --> 25:58.480
We'll

25:58.480 --> 25:59.940
continue investigating.

26:01.310 --> 26:02.550
Where is my aunt?

26:03.070 --> 26:04.550
You mean Xia Changzheng's wife,

26:04.550 --> 26:05.150
Zhang Cui?

26:05.350 --> 26:05.750
Yes.

26:06.110 --> 26:07.200
When we arrived at their house,

26:07.200 --> 26:07.960
she had already fainted.

26:07.960 --> 26:09.260
I think it was from shock.

26:09.260 --> 26:09.880
Right now she's

26:09.880 --> 26:11.140
lying in bed next door.

26:12.680 --> 26:13.880
This is Officer Zhao.

26:14.270 --> 26:15.400
He'll stay in touch with you

26:15.400 --> 26:16.680
about the follow-up.

26:18.030 --> 26:18.440
That's it for now.

26:18.440 --> 26:18.790
Okay.

26:19.240 --> 26:19.640
Okay.

26:20.310 --> 26:21.200
Thank you, sirs.

26:21.200 --> 26:21.860
No problem.

26:24.160 --> 26:26.270
Did you see my cousin?

26:26.750 --> 26:27.750
You have a cousin?

26:28.310 --> 26:28.640
Yes.

26:28.880 --> 26:30.010
Her name is Xia Ziyu.

26:30.070 --> 26:31.510
She studies at a university in Jingcheng

26:31.510 --> 26:33.710
and has already come home for vacation.

26:34.590 --> 26:35.480
I remember

26:35.790 --> 26:37.510
she came to school to find me

26:37.720 --> 26:39.640
on the day when the results came out.

26:39.640 --> 26:40.500
And what did she

26:40.640 --> 26:41.700
say to you that day?

26:48.240 --> 26:48.970
Xia Xiaolan,

26:49.590 --> 26:51.850
you just have to go against me, don't you?

26:53.480 --> 26:54.200
Xia Ziyu,

26:55.000 --> 26:56.270
listen to yourself.

26:57.350 --> 26:59.400
Everyone
can take the college entrance exam.

26:59.400 --> 27:01.130
I got into university on my own.

27:01.310 --> 27:02.970
How is that going against you?

27:03.640 --> 27:05.070
I like Wang Jianhua,

27:05.640 --> 27:07.240
but you had to steal him away.

27:08.070 --> 27:08.880
I got into college

27:08.880 --> 27:10.110
and left that lousy place,

27:10.110 --> 27:11.240
and you had to follow me.

27:11.240 --> 27:13.440
You compete with me for everything I do.

27:13.480 --> 27:14.210
Xia Xiaolan,

27:15.000 --> 27:15.960
why?

27:19.160 --> 27:19.960
Xia Ziyu,

27:21.270 --> 27:23.070
you've really disappointed me.

27:23.550 --> 27:24.680
I thought

27:25.350 --> 27:26.270
I was dealing with

27:26.270 --> 27:27.270
a smart opponent.

27:28.160 --> 27:28.550
I didn't expect you

27:28.550 --> 27:29.920
to be this foolish.

27:30.510 --> 27:31.200
Shut up.

27:32.510 --> 27:33.240
You think

27:33.440 --> 27:35.230
just because you have good grades

27:35.230 --> 27:37.270
and pretend to be obedient
and well‑behaved,

27:37.270 --> 27:39.470
the whole world should make way for you?

27:39.750 --> 27:40.510
Xia Ziyu,

27:40.880 --> 27:42.740
where do you get such confidence?

27:43.030 --> 27:44.830
I didn't compete with you before

27:45.030 --> 27:46.830
because I couldn't be bothered.

27:47.110 --> 27:48.440
The things you treasure

27:48.440 --> 27:50.000
are worthless

27:50.310 --> 27:51.510
to me.

27:53.030 --> 27:54.760
Wang Jianhua? Someone like him

27:55.240 --> 27:57.030
would throw himself at me

27:57.310 --> 27:59.170
without me even lifting a finger.

28:00.310 --> 28:01.110
Xia Ziyu,

28:02.000 --> 28:04.200
maybe you should take a good look
in the mirror

28:04.200 --> 28:06.550
and see how useless you really are.

28:12.310 --> 28:13.790
So you've finally decided to act yourself,

28:13.790 --> 28:14.520
haven't you?

28:16.350 --> 28:17.680
Put away your weakness.

28:18.240 --> 28:19.770
That trick won't work on me.

28:20.150 --> 28:21.510
Show your fangs,

28:21.510 --> 28:23.640
and I might respect you as an opponent.

28:24.400 --> 28:25.110
Xia Ziyu,

28:25.830 --> 28:27.360
I'll tell you one last time—

28:28.190 --> 28:29.950
I never hurt people first,

28:31.640 --> 28:33.720
but if you keep provoking me,

28:34.240 --> 28:35.500
I will never back down.

28:36.160 --> 28:38.290
Whoever made trouble at Blue Phoenix,

28:38.960 --> 28:40.680
whoever spread rumors about me,

28:40.680 --> 28:42.240
and whoever stepped on my wrist—

28:42.240 --> 28:43.750
I won't let any of them off.

28:44.460 --> 28:46.060
And I definitely won't spare

28:46.710 --> 28:49.170
the person pulling the strings
behind them.

28:57.880 --> 28:58.480
Ziyu,

28:59.200 --> 29:00.160
this is the letter of introduction

29:00.160 --> 29:01.160
you asked me to write—

29:01.160 --> 29:02.490
without a destination.

29:04.510 --> 29:06.090
Where are you going that you need

29:06.090 --> 29:08.240
[Letter of Introduction]

29:06.310 --> 29:09.040
a letter of introduction
without a destination?

29:11.160 --> 29:12.350
This is yours. And this is yours.

29:12.350 --> 29:13.680
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

29:13.900 --> 29:14.620
Come often.

29:14.830 --> 29:15.480
Take care.

29:21.350 --> 29:22.350
Fen! Fen!

29:22.920 --> 29:23.650
Look at this!

29:23.790 --> 29:24.440
What?

29:25.270 --> 29:26.350
Look who this is.

29:27.270 --> 29:28.480
Xia Ziyu!

29:28.060 --> 29:30.380
[Case of Top Science Scorer in Yunan Province
Being Attacked Solved Today]

29:29.140 --> 29:30.000
Oh my goodness.

29:30.000 --> 29:31.270
Ziyu's a fugitive now?

29:34.000 --> 29:35.880
The day the police came to our house,

29:35.880 --> 29:37.720
my legs nearly gave out from fear.

29:37.720 --> 29:39.160
That was because of Ziyu?

29:40.000 --> 29:40.480
Isn't it written clearly

29:40.480 --> 29:41.560
in the newspaper?

29:41.750 --> 29:44.210
Xia Ziyu is the mastermind.
The mastermind!

29:44.640 --> 29:45.880
I heard she ran off
with a fake letter of introduction

29:45.880 --> 29:47.340
Wang Jianhua made for her.

29:47.640 --> 29:48.160
Look.

29:48.440 --> 29:49.400
She incited Zhang Erlai

29:49.400 --> 29:50.530
to bully our Xiaolan

29:50.680 --> 29:52.240
and ordered someone to hurt Xiaolan.

29:52.240 --> 29:53.270
With all these charges,

29:53.270 --> 29:55.000
she's going to prison for sure.

29:55.270 --> 29:56.480
This is truly wicked,

29:56.480 --> 29:57.330
doing such things.

29:57.330 --> 29:58.930
Her father was arrested too?

29:59.030 --> 29:59.790
So does that mean no one will

29:59.790 --> 30:01.790
cause trouble for Xiaolan anymore?

30:01.960 --> 30:04.030
Look at what happened to these people.

30:04.030 --> 30:05.070
They wouldn't dare

30:05.070 --> 30:06.130
in a million years.

30:08.030 --> 30:08.400
Mom.

30:08.400 --> 30:08.920
Fen, do you think...

30:08.920 --> 30:09.400
Auntie.

30:11.920 --> 30:12.920
What are you talking about?

30:12.920 --> 30:13.750
Nothing.

30:13.750 --> 30:14.880
N-nothing, really.

30:15.160 --> 30:16.200
N-nothing.

30:16.640 --> 30:17.500
Stop hiding it.

30:18.270 --> 30:18.830
Auntie.

30:20.680 --> 30:21.210
Alright.

30:21.450 --> 30:22.840
I won't pretend with you anymore.

30:22.840 --> 30:23.310
Look.

30:24.000 --> 30:24.680
Xia Ziyu.

30:27.640 --> 30:28.640
Tell me the truth.

30:29.590 --> 30:30.680
Was Xia Ziyu getting arrested

30:30.680 --> 30:31.920
part of your plan?

30:33.180 --> 30:34.550
And that Huang's Rice Bowl place

30:34.550 --> 30:35.550
next to the school—

30:35.550 --> 30:37.750
were you the one who gave them that idea?

30:37.750 --> 30:39.010
And the Zhao brothers—

30:39.110 --> 30:39.920
how did they know

30:39.920 --> 30:41.240
Xia Changzheng had money

30:41.240 --> 30:42.960
after selling the eatery?

30:43.960 --> 30:44.630
Auntie.

30:45.030 --> 30:46.200
I should open

30:46.200 --> 30:46.880
a detective agency for you

30:46.880 --> 30:48.350
next door.

30:49.440 --> 30:50.160
Really?

30:50.160 --> 30:51.450
So I was right?

30:51.480 --> 30:52.480
Detective?

30:52.480 --> 30:53.440
Everything your auntie just said

30:53.440 --> 30:54.310
is true?

30:55.290 --> 30:57.160
Whether it's true or not
doesn't matter anymore.

30:57.160 --> 30:58.400
Hurry and eat this beef

30:58.400 --> 30:59.960
I stewed for 3 hours.

31:00.270 --> 31:01.750
Hot, hot, hot. Hurry.

31:03.270 --> 31:03.800
Xiaolan,

31:04.310 --> 31:05.170
what are these?

31:05.480 --> 31:06.110
Mr. Sun,

31:06.310 --> 31:07.720
these are my study materials

31:07.720 --> 31:09.160
from when I was reviewing.

31:09.160 --> 31:10.760
There are some notes I wrote.

31:10.880 --> 31:11.680
And this one

31:11.680 --> 31:12.920
contains my study methods.

31:12.920 --> 31:13.640
Maybe

31:13.640 --> 31:15.100
they can help the juniors.

31:15.420 --> 31:16.480
Great. Have a seat.

31:16.480 --> 31:16.880
Okay.

31:18.960 --> 31:19.490
Xiaolan.

31:20.000 --> 31:21.530
Is your hand still hurting?

31:21.550 --> 31:23.150
It stopped hurting long ago.

31:24.110 --> 31:25.240
You are

31:25.550 --> 31:26.790
such a proud child.

31:27.030 --> 31:27.860
I know

31:28.020 --> 31:29.880
you've been through a lot before,

31:30.160 --> 31:31.760
and life hasn't been easy for you.

31:31.760 --> 31:33.550
But now you've made it out

31:33.790 --> 31:35.190
through your own effort—

31:35.400 --> 31:37.260
you never have to look back again.

31:37.320 --> 31:38.590
You're a smart child,

31:38.590 --> 31:40.050
so I don't need to say much.

31:40.960 --> 31:41.760
I just wish you

31:42.310 --> 31:43.350
a bright future

31:43.790 --> 31:45.050
and a proud path ahead.

31:46.820 --> 31:47.880
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

31:49.790 --> 31:50.720
Xia Xiaolan!

31:51.480 --> 31:52.480
Registered mail!

31:53.880 --> 31:55.160
Xia Xiaolan!

31:55.640 --> 31:56.640
Registered mail!

31:58.070 --> 31:58.960
Xia Xiaolan!

31:59.440 --> 32:00.440
Registered mail!

32:00.440 --> 32:01.160
Slow down!

32:02.890 --> 32:04.410
It's coming! Hurry!

32:04.440 --> 32:05.200
Hurry up!

32:05.920 --> 32:06.640
Thank you!

32:06.720 --> 32:07.450
Our boss said

32:07.550 --> 32:09.000
your family has been asking every day.

32:09.000 --> 32:09.920
When he saw this,

32:09.920 --> 32:10.550
he told me

32:10.550 --> 32:11.440
to deliver it to you right away.

32:11.440 --> 32:12.770
Your admission letter.

32:12.830 --> 32:14.630
Congratulations, Xia Xiaolan.

32:16.230 --> 32:17.440
Mom, you take it.

32:20.920 --> 32:22.550
Hurry, Fen!

32:25.820 --> 32:26.470
Thank you.

32:26.740 --> 32:27.160
You're welcome.

32:27.160 --> 32:28.240
Fen, open it.

32:28.240 --> 32:29.170
Open it already!

32:35.680 --> 32:38.270
Huaqing University Admission Letter.

32:38.720 --> 32:39.960
Ms. Xiaolan,

32:40.400 --> 32:41.350
you have been approved

32:41.350 --> 32:43.280
for admission to our university's

32:43.400 --> 32:45.400
School of Architecture,
Department of Architecture,

32:45.400 --> 32:47.590
majoring in Architecture.

32:47.920 --> 32:49.920
Please register with this letter

32:49.920 --> 32:52.240
between September 1st

32:52.400 --> 32:55.030
and 10th, 1984.

32:55.790 --> 32:56.750
Bravo!

33:50.030 --> 33:50.920
The 1984

33:50.920 --> 33:52.270
Mathematics college entrance exam

33:52.270 --> 33:53.200
begins now.

33:56.350 --> 33:57.750
Why is math so difficult?

33:59.350 --> 34:00.110
Everything seems

34:00.110 --> 34:01.910
to be going according to my plan,

34:02.440 --> 34:03.750
but only I know

34:04.400 --> 34:05.550
that this math paper

34:06.030 --> 34:08.760
is completely different
from the one I remember.

34:10.670 --> 34:12.480
It feels like a reminder

34:13.320 --> 34:14.510
that everything now

34:14.920 --> 34:16.449
isn't as real as it appears.

34:17.400 --> 34:19.000
I don't know if these changes

34:19.280 --> 34:20.150
will alter

34:20.150 --> 34:21.480
this chapter of my life.

34:57.870 --> 34:59.010
[Admission Letter of Huaqing University]

35:15.670 --> 35:16.110
Fen,

35:16.590 --> 35:17.710
you even pulled out

35:17.710 --> 35:18.960
all of Xiaolan's winter clothes?

35:18.960 --> 35:20.150
Haven't they been stored for a year?

35:20.150 --> 35:20.920
So I'm airing them out

35:20.920 --> 35:22.480
so she can take them when she leaves.

35:22.480 --> 35:22.880
Look.

35:23.480 --> 35:24.400
This is

35:24.400 --> 35:26.110
the new cotton quilt I made for her.

35:26.110 --> 35:27.240
I'll let her take it.

35:28.710 --> 35:29.260
Fengmei,

35:29.440 --> 35:31.440
it's colder in Jingcheng than here.

35:31.800 --> 35:32.400
Should I make her

35:32.400 --> 35:33.530
two padded jackets?

35:34.330 --> 35:35.410
Doesn't she have

35:35.430 --> 35:37.260
that really thick down coat?

35:37.440 --> 35:38.920
Bring that too. It's warm.

35:39.070 --> 35:39.730
Yes, right.

35:40.070 --> 35:40.670
What about...

35:40.670 --> 35:41.480
cotton shoes?

35:41.800 --> 35:43.760
I've packed 3 pairs. Is that enough?

35:43.760 --> 35:44.420
Not enough.

35:44.880 --> 35:45.940
She needs 30 pairs.

35:46.320 --> 35:47.400
30 pairs?

35:49.190 --> 35:49.960
Fen.

35:50.360 --> 35:52.320
She's going to study in a big city.

35:52.550 --> 35:53.510
Who would wear our local

35:53.510 --> 35:54.840
homemade cotton shoes?

35:55.110 --> 35:56.670
How does that saying go?

35:57.710 --> 36:00.110
"A mother worries
when her child travels far."

36:00.110 --> 36:01.510
Look at how anxious you are.

36:01.510 --> 36:02.150
Your child won't start school

36:02.150 --> 36:03.510
for more than a month.

36:03.840 --> 36:04.510
I just...

36:05.320 --> 36:05.960
It's mainly because Xiaolan

36:05.960 --> 36:07.710
has never been away from me for so long.

36:07.710 --> 36:09.590
I'm worried that in Jingcheng, she'll...

36:09.590 --> 36:10.190
Mom.

36:11.670 --> 36:12.200
Xiaolan.

36:15.360 --> 36:15.800
Mom,

36:16.320 --> 36:18.120
let's go to Jingcheng together.

36:22.730 --> 36:23.520
Fen.

36:27.620 --> 36:28.820
Excuse me, excuse me.

36:29.910 --> 36:30.840
Mom, be careful.

36:30.840 --> 36:31.320
Okay.

36:31.890 --> 36:32.720
Excuse me.

36:32.750 --> 36:33.150
Excuse me.

36:33.150 --> 36:34.350
Excuse me, excuse me.

36:35.150 --> 36:36.070
Here, here.

36:36.590 --> 36:37.450
Let me help you.

36:37.710 --> 36:38.360
Thank you.

36:38.360 --> 36:38.710
Okay.

36:39.000 --> 36:39.630
Thanks.

36:40.030 --> 36:41.090
Here, give it to me.

36:42.150 --> 36:42.760
Thank you.

36:42.760 --> 36:43.360
It's okay.

36:43.510 --> 36:44.240
Mom, your...

36:45.990 --> 36:46.520
Alright.

36:46.840 --> 36:47.700
You sit inside.

36:59.360 --> 37:00.460
This is Liu Fen's first time

37:00.460 --> 37:01.860
leaving Shangdu

37:02.480 --> 37:04.550
and boarding a train to Jingcheng.

37:05.880 --> 37:06.320
Mom,

37:07.740 --> 37:08.480
we're off.

37:16.010 --> 37:20.800
[Huaqing University
warmly welcomes newcomers]

37:18.880 --> 37:21.590
A top university
I never even dared to imagine going to—

37:21.590 --> 37:22.630
now I'm actually

37:22.710 --> 37:24.630
going to be a part of it.

37:27.530 --> 37:29.000
After becoming this Xia Xiaolan,

37:29.000 --> 37:30.200
it took me a whole year

37:30.840 --> 37:32.960
to finally climb out of the gutter.

37:33.320 --> 37:34.180
Standing here—

37:35.390 --> 37:36.460
this feeling

37:37.480 --> 37:38.760
is just too amazing!

37:41.440 --> 37:42.170
Ms. Xiaolan,

37:42.760 --> 37:43.800
we're finally

37:44.110 --> 37:45.170
real schoolmates.

37:46.070 --> 37:46.930
Mr. Zhou Cheng,

37:47.230 --> 37:48.840
we must encourage each other

37:49.070 --> 37:51.000
and progress together from now on.

37:59.400 --> 38:00.850
Jingcheng is really different.

38:00.850 --> 38:02.150
The school is huge.

38:03.550 --> 38:04.400
Excuse us!

38:04.400 --> 38:04.800
Mom!

38:05.510 --> 38:06.280
Wait for me.

38:11.480 --> 38:12.760
So that's how

38:13.070 --> 38:14.330
my college life began.

38:14.480 --> 38:16.280
Everyone, attention! Eyes right!

38:15.370 --> 38:18.910
[1984, Freshman]

38:18.110 --> 38:19.280
Eyes front!

38:19.840 --> 38:20.320
At ease!

38:21.440 --> 38:22.190
Attention!

38:22.960 --> 38:23.880
Right face!

38:35.060 --> 38:38.870
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

38:39.200 --> 38:39.960
Xiaolan? Is that Xiaolan?

38:39.960 --> 38:40.590
It's Xiaolan!

38:40.140 --> 38:42.620
♪ Let my heart boil ♪

38:40.670 --> 38:41.470
It's Xiaolan!

38:43.410 --> 38:45.710
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

38:48.530 --> 38:52.150
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

38:51.020 --> 38:52.140
Jingcheng is huge,

38:52.670 --> 38:53.660
and Huaqing is huge.

38:53.660 --> 38:56.090
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

38:54.480 --> 38:55.880
Under the school's halo,

38:56.120 --> 38:59.610
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

38:56.320 --> 38:57.480
even someone as small as me

38:57.480 --> 38:58.960
was lucky enough to take part

38:58.960 --> 39:00.430
in many major events of the era.

39:00.430 --> 39:02.570
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

39:01.230 --> 39:02.670
These stunning scenes

39:03.150 --> 39:04.190
gradually made me forget

39:03.770 --> 39:06.340
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

39:04.190 --> 39:06.120
I was a traveler from another time,

39:06.320 --> 39:07.180
and I started to see myself

39:07.180 --> 39:09.590
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

39:07.400 --> 39:08.880
as part of this era.

39:10.310 --> 39:15.190
♪ Our youth ♪

39:13.270 --> 39:15.170
The grand opening!

39:15.210 --> 39:18.740
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

39:16.410 --> 39:20.750
[Blue Phoenix No.1 Branch in Jingcheng]

39:18.760 --> 39:22.140
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

39:21.590 --> 39:25.030
[1985, Sophomore]

39:22.320 --> 39:25.160
♪ We never give up ♪

39:25.070 --> 39:25.760
Bravo!

39:25.780 --> 39:29.000
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

39:26.190 --> 39:26.840
Xia Xiaolan!

39:26.840 --> 39:28.070
Great job! Excellent!

39:28.070 --> 39:28.880
Excellent!

39:29.020 --> 39:32.250
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

39:32.280 --> 39:35.670
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

39:35.700 --> 39:38.750
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

39:36.400 --> 39:37.660
-Amazing.
-Thank you.

39:39.220 --> 39:42.160
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

39:42.530 --> 39:48.510
♪ That'd be enough ♪

39:56.110 --> 39:57.590
Everyone has submitted their proposals.

39:56.160 --> 39:59.740
♪ We'll get hurt when we grow up ♪

39:58.190 --> 39:58.840
However,

39:59.110 --> 40:00.590
for this museum project,

40:01.000 --> 40:01.630
there are only two spots

40:01.250 --> 40:03.870
♪ Away from home ♪

40:02.110 --> 40:03.310
for undergraduates.

40:04.390 --> 40:07.060
♪ Are you alright? ♪

40:08.280 --> 40:09.840
After the design team's evaluation,

40:08.850 --> 40:13.210
♪ I'm not willing to be ordinary ♪

40:10.510 --> 40:11.230
I announce

40:11.670 --> 40:13.410
that the students selected are...

40:13.410 --> 40:14.190
Xia Xiaolan

40:14.590 --> 40:15.280
and Ning Xue.

40:14.760 --> 40:20.750
♪ Sometimes I want to go crazy.
Once you've made up your mind, be brave ♪

40:15.590 --> 40:18.550
College life is simple yet full.

40:19.630 --> 40:21.480
Like any ordinary college student,

40:21.480 --> 40:22.400
the more I learn,

40:21.520 --> 40:23.560
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

40:22.590 --> 40:24.590
the more I realize how little I know.

40:24.910 --> 40:27.130
♪ There are laughter and tears ♪

40:25.320 --> 40:26.320
I grab every chance I have

40:26.320 --> 40:28.030
to study and practice.

40:28.110 --> 40:28.630
Here we go.

40:28.210 --> 40:31.010
♪ There's joy and sorrow ♪

40:28.920 --> 40:31.110
3, 2, 1!

40:31.300 --> 40:34.340
♪ But this is life ♪

40:32.150 --> 40:32.630
Guys.

40:35.030 --> 40:36.090
You two, like this.

40:36.320 --> 40:39.950
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

40:36.800 --> 40:38.550
Put it like this. Bend a little.

40:38.590 --> 40:39.320
Yes.

40:39.970 --> 40:43.270
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

40:40.070 --> 40:40.930
Just like this.

40:43.300 --> 40:46.200
♪ We never give up ♪

40:46.440 --> 40:47.880
The museum project our teacher led us

40:47.020 --> 40:50.150
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

40:47.590 --> 40:50.600
[1986, Junior]

40:47.880 --> 40:48.880
to participate in

40:49.110 --> 40:50.440
won a national award.

40:50.170 --> 40:53.390
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

40:50.880 --> 40:52.510
I might even have a chance

40:52.510 --> 40:53.440
to apply

40:53.420 --> 40:56.640
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

40:53.660 --> 40:55.000
to graduate a year early.

40:55.000 --> 40:55.800
That's great!

40:56.070 --> 40:56.590
Then we can

40:56.590 --> 40:57.230
graduate together.

40:57.010 --> 40:59.950
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

41:00.150 --> 41:00.710
Xiaolan.

41:00.330 --> 41:03.190
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

41:02.880 --> 41:03.700
This Spring Festival...

41:03.700 --> 41:10.090
♪ That'd be enough ♪

41:03.960 --> 41:05.420
can I invite you to my home?

41:06.230 --> 41:07.960
Besides studying and business,

41:07.960 --> 41:08.840
I also have some

41:08.960 --> 41:11.760
sweet troubles
I'm not very good at handling.

41:14.880 --> 41:15.710
Uncles, aunts,

41:15.710 --> 41:16.420
grandpa, grandma,

41:16.420 --> 41:17.150
happy New Year.

41:17.150 --> 41:18.190
Happy New Year.

41:18.280 --> 41:19.030
Great.

41:20.240 --> 41:23.750
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

41:23.780 --> 41:27.220
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

41:27.350 --> 41:30.090
♪ We never give up ♪

41:30.750 --> 41:34.010
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

41:31.840 --> 41:32.280
Mom.

41:32.840 --> 41:33.570
Stop wiping.

41:33.710 --> 41:34.670
Come on, I'll take you somewhere.

41:34.040 --> 41:37.140
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

41:35.000 --> 41:35.800
Where?

41:35.960 --> 41:37.160
You'll see when we get there.

41:37.160 --> 41:40.770
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

41:37.190 --> 41:37.550
Let's go.

41:37.550 --> 41:38.760
So mysterious.

41:39.760 --> 41:40.290
Let's go.

41:40.800 --> 41:46.030
♪ That'd be enough ♪

41:41.550 --> 41:43.880
Sometimes I instinctively remember

41:44.320 --> 41:45.510
that this could be a dream,

41:44.990 --> 41:48.020
[Blue Phoenix No.1 Branch in Jingcheng]

41:46.150 --> 41:47.480
and I have to plan ahead.

41:48.480 --> 41:50.930
[Property Certificate in Jingcheng]

41:50.000 --> 41:50.630
From now on,

41:50.630 --> 41:52.320
this will be our house.

41:53.070 --> 41:54.190
You bought it?

41:55.230 --> 41:56.480
You're wasting money again.

41:56.480 --> 41:57.750
How much did this cost?

41:57.960 --> 41:59.490
This isn't a waste of money.

41:59.800 --> 42:00.930
It's an investment.

42:01.280 --> 42:03.830
This house will be
worth a fortune in the future.

42:03.830 --> 42:04.490
Promise me,

42:04.590 --> 42:05.320
unless absolutely necessary,

42:05.320 --> 42:06.120
never sell it.

42:07.400 --> 42:08.230
In case I...

42:11.030 --> 42:11.690
Never mind.

42:11.800 --> 42:13.600
Anyway, just don't ever sell it.

42:14.960 --> 42:16.420
I promise. I won't sell it.

42:16.960 --> 42:17.800
Most of the time,

42:17.680 --> 42:19.340
[1987, Senior]

42:17.920 --> 42:19.220
I simply don't think about anything

42:19.220 --> 42:20.470
and go with my heart.

42:19.340 --> 42:21.000
[Finals of the First
National College English Competition]

42:21.440 --> 42:22.880
However, from time to time,

42:22.880 --> 42:25.210
unexpected problems pop up, reminding me

42:25.480 --> 42:26.440
that some things

42:26.960 --> 42:28.560
aren't completely settled.

42:32.470 --> 42:33.330
Over here, Mom.

42:33.840 --> 42:35.040
Mom. Here. Over here.

42:41.070 --> 42:42.840
There are quite a lot of people here.

42:42.840 --> 42:44.840
Good thing
we got tickets from Mrs. Zhang in advance.

42:44.840 --> 42:46.760
Right,
otherwise we wouldn't have gotten in.

42:46.760 --> 42:47.440
Zhou Cheng.

42:48.360 --> 42:50.590
Does Xiaolan know we're coming today?

42:51.590 --> 42:53.070
I told him not to tell her.

42:53.190 --> 42:54.550
The competition is stressful enough.

42:54.550 --> 42:56.480
Let's not affect the kid's performance.

42:56.480 --> 42:56.880
Right.

42:57.230 --> 42:57.880
Alright, miss.

42:57.880 --> 42:59.030
Wait over there for the interview.

42:59.030 --> 42:59.960
Okay, thank you.

43:01.080 --> 43:01.920
Contestant No.12.

43:01.920 --> 43:02.590
We're over here.

43:02.590 --> 43:03.630
-No.12 is here.
-No.12, please

43:03.630 --> 43:05.290
get ready for your interview.

43:05.360 --> 43:06.630
Who's the teacher leading

43:06.630 --> 43:07.150
the Huaqing University team?

43:07.150 --> 43:07.800
I am.

43:08.490 --> 43:09.320
Please come with me.

43:09.320 --> 43:10.510
The judging committee

43:10.510 --> 43:11.400
wants to ask you about a few things.

43:11.400 --> 43:11.840
Okay.

43:12.230 --> 43:12.710
You go ahead with the interview.

43:12.710 --> 43:13.630
I'll be right back.

43:13.630 --> 43:14.000
Okay.

43:14.000 --> 43:14.600
Good luck.

43:15.070 --> 43:16.200
Come on, have a seat.

43:16.230 --> 43:17.070
Let's keep it cheerful.

43:17.070 --> 43:17.480
Okay.

43:18.360 --> 43:19.550
Please introduce yourself.

43:19.550 --> 43:20.510
Come on, get ready to...

43:20.510 --> 43:22.030
-Hold on.
-Hello, everyone.

43:22.030 --> 43:23.160
No need to film this.

43:23.440 --> 43:24.000
It won't be aired anyway.

43:24.000 --> 43:24.600
Excuse me,

43:24.760 --> 43:25.400
sir.

43:25.710 --> 43:26.630
I'd like to ask—

43:27.000 --> 43:28.230
everyone else has taken the interview,

43:28.230 --> 43:29.550
why did it stop at me?

43:30.280 --> 43:31.480
Miss, don't misunderstand.

43:31.480 --> 43:33.480
We certainly have nothing against you.

43:33.480 --> 43:35.210
This is our leader's decision.

43:35.910 --> 43:37.370
Let's move to the next one.

43:38.480 --> 43:39.070
Sir.

43:39.510 --> 43:41.110
I come from the countryside.

43:41.150 --> 43:42.840
I usually just focus on studying

43:42.840 --> 43:44.590
and I'm not very familiar
with social rules.

43:44.590 --> 43:45.630
Can you tell me

43:46.030 --> 43:47.190
if I offended

43:47.190 --> 43:48.440
any important leader?

43:48.440 --> 43:50.280
I worked so hard to reach this final.

43:50.280 --> 43:52.140
I don't want to fail for no reason.

43:55.230 --> 43:55.670
Fine.

43:56.030 --> 43:58.230
You'll find out sooner or later anyway.

43:58.230 --> 44:01.630
It's Wang Guangping, president
of the English Association.

44:02.030 --> 44:02.400
I see.

44:02.400 --> 44:02.920
Next one, please.

44:02.920 --> 44:04.190
Alright, let's move on to the next one.

